⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Horn of Valere
node WOT · WOT · ⟦The Horn of Valere:WOT:f3c1f8⟧

WHO   — The Horn of Valere — the horn that calls the dead heroes back
WHAT  — The legendary horn that, when sounded, summons back the Heroes of the Horn to fight for the one who blew it.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: The cosmology — the turning Wheel and its prophecy-objects  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — It is one of the great prophecy-objects of the turning Wheel, a thread the Pattern reserves for the final reckoning.
HOW   — Its call reaches across the Ages to the great champions the Wheel spins out, binding them to its blower — save at the Last Battle, when they answer only the Light.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Blow, and the dead heroes ride to your banner — until the last dawn, when they ride only for the Light.

